          : 'The board wants momentum. Your competitors are announcing AI initiatives. The pressure to commit is real and immediate — but nobody in the room is asking whether the underlying assumption is correct.'}</p>
      </li>
      <li class="problem__card fade-up">
        <span class="problem__card-number" aria-hidden="true">02</span>
        <h3 class="problem__card-title">{isDE ? 'Niemand wird dafür bezahlt, Nein zu sagen.' : 'Nobody in the room is paid to say no.'}</h3>
